@mheon Yes a similar issue but not the same. Here it seems the the port forwarding generally works but sometimes will respond with ECONNRESET. However in the compose CI test the port forwarder setup fails, no retry will make it work.

@holgerpieta you could try creating the container with `--network=slirp4netns:port_handler=slirp4netns`
This will use the a different port forwarder. Also it might be worth to try with a mtu of 1500, `--network=slirp4netns:port_handler=slirp4netns,mtu=1500`. The default port_handler is rootlesskit and the default mtu is 65520.
